  "sections": [
    {
      "title": { "de": "Spickzettel", "en": "Cheat sheet" },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "note",
          "text": {
            "de": "Vier Optionen, von schlank zu voll: Grundton · Oktave (Grundton + Grundton) · Shell (Grundton + Quinte) · Voll (Grundton + Quinte + Terz, Terz eine Oktave höher). Je tiefer, desto weniger Töne. Umkehrungen des vollen Voicings: Grundstellung = Grundton im Bass · 1. Umkehrung = Terz im Bass · 2. Umkehrung = Quinte im Bass. Bei Moll wird nur die Terz im vollen Voicing einen Halbton kleiner. Mehrere Töne mit Komma trennen — die Reihenfolge ist egal. Die erste Zeile jeder Übung ist ein Beispiel.",
            "en": "Four options, lean to full: root · octave (root + root) · shell (root + fifth) · full (root + fifth + third, third an octave higher). The lower, the fewer notes. Inversions of the full voicing: root position = root in the bass · 1st inversion = third in the bass · 2nd inversion = fifth in the bass. In minor only the third of the full voicing drops a semitone. Separate several notes with a comma — order doesn't matter. The first row of each exercise is an example."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": { "de": "Übung 1: Welche Option passt?", "en": "Exercise 1: which option fits?" },
      "intro": { "de": "Lies die Situation und wähl die beste Bass-Option (Grundton, Oktave, Shell oder Voll).", "en": "Read the situation and pick the best bass option (root, octave, shell or full)." },
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "table",
          "head": [ {"de":"Lage / Wunsch","en":"Register / wish"},{"de":"beste Option","en":"best option"} ],
          "rows": [
            [ {"de":"Sehr tief — nur ein Ton","en":"Very low — just one note"},{"de":"Grundton","en":"Root"} ],
            [ {"de":"Tief, mehr Wucht — zwei Töne, gleicher Name","en":"Low, more weight — two notes, same name"},{"de":"","en":""} ],
            [ {"de":"Tief und offen, ohne Terz","en":"Low and open, no third"},{"de":"","en":""} ],
            [ {"de":"Mittig, warm und komplett","en":"Mid, warm and complete"},{"de":"","en":""} ],
            [ {"de":"Ganz unten, soll nicht matschen","en":"Right at the bottom, must not get muddy"},{"de":"","en":""} ],
            [ {"de":"Höhere Lage, voller Klang erlaubt","en":"Higher register, full sound allowed"},{"de":"","en":""} ]
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "solution", "label": { "de": "Lösungen anzeigen", "en": "Show solutions" },
          "blocks": [{
